\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fclinicaltrials.gov%2Fct2%2Fshow%2FNCT03719586&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwdjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=2bf9e11c\" target=\"_blank\">https://clinicaltrials.gov/ct2/show/NCT03719586</a><br />\nPMO除左DMD之外未試過人體當antiviral用，無safety data應該唔會而家攞黎試<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5920040/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC5920040%2F&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwdjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=c5ea5232\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5920040/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597775dce2a5b52ea1b21a71f41d77eca4c41fec","tid":1867613,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c69dbd1e66c0ce5027fe4defbb79ef2d1ee614ab","tid":1867613,"uid":264433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:26:17.000Z","msg":"LM學嘢<br />\nsend左比supervisor問意見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:45:21.000Z","msg":"如果佢覆咗 講埋俾我聽啦 thx 巴打"},{"pid":"8c6bf581dd09c05a8969a106f71f39c1e1805648","tid":1867613,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5c4913854c460fe1e371721654904190bd02a83","tid":1867613,"uid":337021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f1b7d34cba4423020e0e30f8ae94a3d13e6960bb","tid":1867613,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:52:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://link.springer.com/content/pdf/10.1007%2F978-0-387-33012-9_103.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Fcontent%2Fpdf%2F10.1007%252F978-0-387-33012-9_103.pdf&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwdjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=b616174b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://link.springer.com/content/pdf/10.1007%2F978-0-387-33012-9_103.pdf</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:41:05.000Z","msg":"我唔太熟隻野，不過我估應該太新<br />\n用Remdesivir應該都係因為之前做Ebola已經做緊 phase I<br />\n<a href=\"https://clinicaltrials.gov/ct2/show/NCT03719586\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fclinicaltrials.gov%2Fct2%2Fshow%2FNCT03719586&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwdjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=2bf9e11c\" target=\"_blank\">https://clinicaltrials.gov/ct2/show/NCT03719586</a><br />\nPMO除左DMD之外未試過人體當antiviral用，無safety data應該唔會而家攞黎試<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5920040/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC5920040%2F&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwdjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=c5ea5232\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5920040/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:58:12.000Z","msg":"但係pmo唔係sars開始已經研究緊咩 雖然冇仔細search有冇human test 巴打可唔可以幫手問吓其他熟悉呢樣嘢嘅人<br />\n同埋pmo同remdesivir應該都係generally applicable to所有/大部分coronavirus?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"257bb1a4fe5e86dffdaaffd9f919fc09b6b59773","tid":1867613,"uid":125312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:00:42.000Z","msg":"似喺同RNAi有差唔多通病，例如in vivo efficacy 唔高同會off-target <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有佢文中都有提到RNA virus  mutate 得好快，而佢in vitro嘅七代目已經發現到resistances ，而又喺十一代目到confirm左mutation。所以就算work都好都要不停咁轉PMO 個sequence 去 adapt 個mutation <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em>However, an increase in titer indicative of partial resistance was observed after seven passages. SARS-CoV plaque purified after 11 rounds of TRS2 P-PMO selection formed small plaques on Vero-E6 cells in the absence of P-PMO (Fig. 2B). </em>"},{"pid":"f093e5669019bb9e490ec3ea7b54c159cce16ba6","tid":1867613,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"257bb1a4fe5e86dffdaaffd9f919fc09b6b59773","tid":1867613,"uid":125312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:00:42.000Z","msg":"似喺同RNAi有差唔多通病，例如in vivo efficacy 唔高同會off-target <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有佢文中都有提到RNA virus  mutate 得好快，而佢in vitro嘅七代目已經發現到resistances ，而又喺十一代目到confirm左mutation。所以就算work都好都要不停咁轉PMO 個sequence 去 adapt 個mutation <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em>However, an increase in titer indicative of partial resistance was observed after seven passages. SARS-CoV plaque purified after 11 rounds of TRS2 P-PMO selection formed small plaques on Vero-E6 cells in the absence of P-PMO (Fig. 2B). </em>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:05:03.000Z","msg":"但係用remdesivir就唔會有mutation同drug resistance 呢個問題？"},{"pid":"72c8abc5c5b7b5fec68fcf17d91fda219c2ff24d","tid":1867613,"uid":125312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f093e5669019bb9e490ec3ea7b54c159cce16ba6","tid":1867613,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"257bb1a4fe5e86dffdaaffd9f919fc09b6b59773","tid":1867613,"uid":125312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:00:42.000Z","msg":"似喺同RNAi有差唔多通病，例如in vivo efficacy 唔高同會off-target <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有佢文中都有提到RNA virus  mutate 得好快，而佢in vitro嘅七代目已經發現到resistances ，而又喺十一代目到confirm左mutation。所以就算work都好都要不停咁轉PMO 個sequence 去 adapt 個mutation <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em>However, an increase in titer indicative of partial resistance was observed after seven passages. SARS-CoV plaque purified after 11 rounds of TRS2 P-PMO selection formed small plaques on Vero-E6 cells in the absence of P-PMO (Fig. 2B). </em>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:05:03.000Z","msg":"但係用remdesivir就唔會有mutation同drug resistance 呢個問題？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:21:53.000Z","msg":"冇睇過Remdesivir 詳細個mechanism，但喺PMO呢類RNA therapy 要 target specific 先有效。如果病毒本身個sequence 一特變左就會bind唔穩又或者唔中target<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n份文有講佢第十一代突變左3粒rna已經改變哂成個efficacy 了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9697e0afa1f3d9f32a0abbb5ccc0119f69e147e","tid":1867613,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T13:18:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">手足裝備抗沙士：防毒面具（型號/分析/用法/清潔全齊）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請大家幫手推一推，正個評</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1861825\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1861825</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請大家幫手正評，避免沉底"},{"pid":"7c9889d3680fed0f30865a9a826b55bf7fc40d8a","tid":1867613,"uid":348453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T13:45:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d5ccddd2316acfaba7d37aa2a919e2802195588f","tid":1867613,"uid":348453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T13:50:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef7e61f485b4513ce302286addbb4d6f1c0bffa3","tid":1867613,"uid":331861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T03:48:26.000Z","msg":"我諗其實呢個問題應該要問返政治家先啱<br />\n老實講今次肺炎從來唔係無辦法去解決<br />\n而係有人無腦兼想報復姐"}]}